		<div class="container-fluid paragraph content textbox">
			<h3>How The Club Operates</h3>
		<div class="container-fluid">
			<p>By now you have hopefully read about all the great stuff the club does, and all about the fantastic sport of gliding, and have been persuaded to sign up. If so, you'll probably want to find out how the club does what it does, and how we get people flying and on all our trips. This page is intended to tell you exactly how!</p>
